  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Ephemeral wisps of nature spirits dance about those you strike.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Nature Magic or the ability to cast druid or ranger spells; Vital Strike, Knowledge (nature) 5 ranks.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you use Vital Strike (or Improved Vital Strike or Greater Vital Strike), the creature you hit with the attack must succeed at a Will save (DC = 10 + 1/2 your character level + your Wisdom modifier) or be illuminated as if by faerie fire for 1 minute. You can use this benefit a number of times per day equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1).<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When using this feat, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to increase the DC of the effect by an amount equal to the number of stamina points you spent.",
